            bindings = <
                  &kp Q  &kp W           &kp E           &kp R        &kp T        &kp Y          &kp U        &kp I            &kp O            &kp P
                  &kp A  &mt LEFT_GUI S  &mt LEFT_ALT D  &mt LSHFT F  &kp G        &kp H          &mt RSHFT J  &mt RIGHT_ALT K  &mt RIGHT_GUI L  &kp SEMI
&mt LCTRL ESCAPE  &kp Z  &kp X           &kp C           &mt LCTRL V  &kp B        &kp N          &mt RCTRL M  &kp COMMA        &kp DOT          &kp FSLH  &kp SINGLE_QUOTE
                                         &kp DEL         &lt 1 TAB    &kp SPACE    &kp BACKSPACE  &lt 2 ENTER  &kp ESCAPE
            >;
